<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6521538>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–7. Synanthedon suhua sp. nov., Scale bar = 5 mm. 2–3 Male, holotype, TAIWAN: PINGTUNG (NHM). 4–5 Male, paratype, TAIWAN: PINGTUNG (NTNU). 6–7 Female, paratype, TAIWAN: HSINCHU (NTNU)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6521538/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6521540>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–11. Genitalia of Synanthedon suhua sp. nov. 8 Caudal view of tegumen-uncus and valvae. 9 Lateral view of phallus. 10 Distal part of phallus. 11 Female genitalia. Scale bar = 0.5 mm for 8, 9, and 11; 0.1mm for 10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6521540/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6521542>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–14. Biology of Synanthedon suhua sp. nov. 12 Male adult in resting position on leaf of Lithocarpus corneus (image taken by Yi-Ting Chung). 13 Freshly emerged female adult. 14 Pupal exuviae protruding from trunk of Quercus longinux." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6521542/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

